--- !u!114 &11400000
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 70c970a7d9f7d414994564bd048e8a6d, type: 3}
  m_Name: Generic_Credible
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: KBTV.Runtime::KBTV.Dialogue.CallerDialogueTemplate
  Topic: {fileID: 0}
  Legitimacy: 2
  Priority: 0
  Length: 10
  IntroLines:
  - Text: Vern, I've been a listener for years. I finally have something worth sharing.
    Tone: 0
    Weight: 1
  - Text: I'm not one to call in, but what I witnessed deserves attention.
    Tone: 0
    Weight: 1
  - Text: I've documented everything. Photos, dates, times. This is real.
    Tone: 1
    Weight: 1
  DetailLines:
  - Text: I observed it for several minutes. Enough time to rule out the obvious
      explanations.
    Tone: 0
    Weight: 1
  - Text: Multiple witnesses corroborated what I saw. Independent accounts, same
      details.
    Tone: 0
    Weight: 1
  - Text: I've researched similar cases. The pattern is consistent.
    Tone: 1
    Weight: 1
  DefenseLines:
  - Text: I've considered every conventional explanation. None of them fit.
    Tone: 0
    Weight: 1
  - Text: I'm a rational person, Vern. This defies rational explanation.
    Tone: 0
    Weight: 1
  - Text: The evidence speaks for itself.
    Tone: 0
    Weight: 1
  AcceptanceLines:
  - Text: Thank you. It means a lot to be taken seriously.
    Tone: 1
    Weight: 1
  - Text: That's exactly why I called your show.
    Tone: 0
    Weight: 1
  - Text: I knew your listeners would understand.
    Tone: 1
    Weight: 1
  ExtraDetailLines:
  - Text: There's more to this story. The follow-up investigation revealed even stranger
      details.
    Tone: 0
    Weight: 1
  - Text: I've been in contact with others who experienced the same thing. The similarities
      are uncanny.
    Tone: 1
    Weight: 1
  - Text: What I haven't told you yet is what happened the next day.
    Tone: 0
    Weight: 1
  ExtraDefenseLines: []
  ConclusionLines:
  - Text: I'll send you what I've gathered. People should see this.
    Tone: 0
    Weight: 1
  - Text: Keep doing what you do, Vern. It matters.
    Tone: 0
    Weight: 1
  - Text: I'll keep investigating and report back.
    Tone: 1
    Weight: 1
